      "role": "user",
      "content": "right, so it sounds like it's really about them being sneaky and manipulative to get what they want. it's kind of creepy how they can just lurk around the internet to find all that stuff. do you have any advice on how we can describe the \"mindset\" of these attackers to our staff? like, how should we frame their behavior so employees understand the level of deception they're dealing with?",
